{"tid":745812,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"「警世文」中學雞請好好珍惜校園生活","createTime":"2018-07-17T05:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T05:58:47.000Z","uid":71508,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd987ce052fca63b8c5567af3a541c8b27433db6","tid":745812,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"呢類型既文章，應該已經有好多人都講過類似既野 <br />\n不過都係有感而發想講下，希望你地唔好第時先黎後悔。 <br />\n<br />\n仲讀緊書既中學雞，好好珍惜你家陣既校園生活。青春過去就冇架啦。 <br />\n以我個人為例，好多知心好友都係中學果陣識的。 <br />\n每個人都只係一個普通人，唔好怕浪費自己既人生， <br />\n唔洗因為自己既背景而自卑，要記住，你唔會係最差既一個 <br />\n唔好以為努力可以改變一切，呢D只會出現係電視既橋段，現實係少有機會發生的。 <br />\n當然我唔係叫人偷懶，但努力和成果唔一定成正比的，希望你地明白到呢個現實。 <br />\n<br />\n年少係輕狂既，唔好太在意他人既睇法， <br />\n趁你仲有行動力，冇乜顧慮既時侯，有咩想做就去做啦！唔好等到第時先黎後悔。 <br />\n年輕人係幼稚架啦，無問題架。唔洗好似大人咁，想幼稚下都要懼怕他人既目光。 <br />\n就算真係做得唔好，過多幾年最多都係比人話你年少輕狂或者幼稚。 <br />\n因為做左而後悔，總比乜都無做而後悔好。 <br />\n<br />\n考完DSE既， <br />\n如果你打算讀上去，家陣可能已經搵緊暑期工 <br />\n當然，趁有時間，當係見識下世面，了解到賺錢既辛苦係好既。 <br />\n但最好留返D時間做下其他事， <br />\n呢個可能係你第一次有咁大舊錢洗既時間 <br />\n但同時亦都可能係你最後一次有一段長時間既假期 <br />\n要記住，人生流流長，唔洗咁急就去工作。 <br />\n第時大把機會比你工作，做到你退休果日都仲得。 <br />\n為左果少少錢，其實根本唔值得你犧牲咁多 <br />\n當然，最緊要係唔好令自己後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，記得要拍拖食女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b9fbd831fbde9f0d42061208d1116e5146a56c","tid":745812,"uid":170668,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:03:17.000Z","msg":"中學冇溝過女是否人生遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7aee7d047bd9ef5084f8d869e9a9faa91060c08","tid":745812,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e1b9fbd831fbde9f0d42061208d1116e5146a56c","tid":745812,"uid":170668,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:03:17.000Z","msg":"中學冇溝過女是否人生遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"絕對係"},{"pid":"0edc73e0cb4a15d95853824e1da62d220d2a875e","tid":745812,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d7aee7d047bd9ef5084f8d869e9a9faa91060c08","tid":745812,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e1b9fbd831fbde9f0d42061208d1116e5146a56c","tid":745812,"uid":170668,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:03:17.000Z","msg":"中學冇溝過女是否人生遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"絕對係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:04:17.000Z","msg":"太毒冇計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b30c13af9ac4083db08cd38a4b28a229d7b9c1","tid":745812,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b80fc03627abadf181fd2bca94de3005ff8d220","tid":745812,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:16:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1357e67786623eb9bc4571c1dce2d960fb23e88","tid":745812,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:20:36.000Z","msg":"最後一句先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc4043dfeef17621eb2e0e5ce11e8f20c5a400c","tid":745812,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:42:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30650c01a36ed8c1ee11af2a93831845a180f7e7","tid":745812,"uid":23874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9a583a3bb1e224bdbec434703bc2f1fcb69c69","tid":745812,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30650c01a36ed8c1ee11af2a93831845a180f7e7","tid":745812,"uid":23874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:47:50.000Z","m